{"name":"Apple Balsamic Pork Chops","slug":"apple-balsamic-pork-chops","description":"","ingredients":[{"name":"oil","quantity":"2 tbsp ","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"center-cut fast fry pork loin chops","quantity":"1 lb (450 g)","additionalInstruction":"about 4 small chops"},{"name":"large apple ","quantity":"1","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Vegetable Broth or Nourish Broth ","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> cup prepared ","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Vegetable Broth Mix","quantity":"1 <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> tsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"boiling water","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Nourish Broth Mix","quantity":"1 <sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>2</sub> tsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"boiling water","quantity":"1 cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"apple juice ","quantity":"<sup>1</sup>&frasl;<sub>4</sub> cup","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"balsamic vinegar","quantity":"1 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"Balsamic Vinaigrette Dressing Mix ","quantity":"2 tsp","additionalInstruction":null},{"name":"butter","quantity":"1 tbsp","additionalInstruction":null}],"totalTime":"20 min","servings":"4 servings","preparation":"<ol>\n  <li>Heat oil in a large frying&nbsp;pan over medium-high heat. Add pork chops; fry until browned,&nbsp;about&nbsp;2–3 min per side. Remove from pan and keep warm.&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Meanwhile, core and thinly slice apple.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Add sliced apple, broth, juice, vinegar, and dressing mix to pan, stirring to loosen brown bits.&nbsp;Simmer, 2 min, until apples have softened slightly.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li>\n  <li>Return&nbsp;pork&nbsp;to pan. Cover and simmer until meat is cooked through, about&nbsp;3–4&nbsp;min,&nbsp;turning once.&nbsp;Place pork on plates. Add butter to sauce;&nbsp;stir until melted.&nbsp;Spoon on top of pork.&nbsp;</li>\n</ol>","tags":[{"slug":"sugar_conscious","name":"Sugar Conscious"},{"slug":"gluten